               "text": "### Images from Athens\n\nThese images are copyright for Athens and allowed to be used according to the license determined by them.\n\nTo visualize all images, use the left and right arrows on the slide below.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 3</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgAthens\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAthens', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Erechtheion Temple in Athens, Greece (<htcite0>). Photo taken on <htdate0>, during a visit to the site.</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Cultures and Civilization - Is there a hierarchy between them? (<htcite1>)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 3</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"img5\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img5', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Columns at the Parthenon, Greece (<htcite4>). Photo taken on <htdate1>, during a visit to the archaeological site.</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Continuity: When we look around us and at ourselves, we don't see holes everywhere. In this text, we begin to understand how to connect things (<htcite2>).</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 3</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"img0\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('img0', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Prison of Socrates, Athens, Greece (<htcite5>). Photo taken on <htdate2>, during a visit to the archaeological site.</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Understanding it as...: In this text, we begin to explore the understanding of philosophy (<htcite3>).</li></ul></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
